@startuml
title Error Normalization (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FCFCFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #424242
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B3E5FC
component "AthenaGatewayError" as GatewayError #FFCCBC
component "normalizeAthenaError()" as Normalize #FFE082
component "kind classifier\n(unique/auth/rate/transient/...)" as KindClassifier #FFF59D
component "AthenaResult envelope" as Result #DCE775

Consumer --> Result : Read { data, error, status }
Consumer --> GatewayError : Catch thrown gateway errors
GatewayError --> Normalize : Convert for helpers/hooks
Result --> Normalize : Convert result failures
Normalize --> KindClassifier
KindClassifier --> Consumer : { kind, message, status, raw }

note right of Normalize
No first-class error code/category constants.
end note
@enduml
